&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee-Owned Advantage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;EnSafe is 100% employee-owned, with an ESOP (Employee Stock Ownership Plan) since 1997. That means when EnSafe succeeds, you succeed too, turning

