&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5 years of administrative assistant experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience with Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Adobe Acrobat, PowerPoint).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be a highly organized and meticulous individual; able to collaborate effectively with multiple offices at one time, manage multiple tasks and assignments; ability to work with strict deadlines/under pressure, have a pleasant, can-do attitude, and use critical thinking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A college degree is a plus but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
