&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Do you like working with different project teams in a fast-paced environment? Are you interested in joining an organization focused on making a positive impact? If so, we’d like to talk with you about growing with us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking a full-time &lt;strong&gt;Assistant Project Manager, Environmental Scientist or Geologist &lt;/strong&gt;for our Jacksonville, FL; Pensacola, FL; or Tampa, FL office. This is an excellent opportunity to join and grow EnSafe, getting involved in a variety of projects for a diverse range of clients across the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
