&lt;li&gt;Strong working knowledge of OSHA regulations and practical safety program implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing written safety programs, procedures, training content, reports, or similar technical documents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort presenting information and delivering training to groups with varying levels of safety knowledge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability

